'''梨形糖果Pear drops''' 是英國由糖和香料製成的硬糖。經典梨形糖果一半是粉紅色和一半是黃色，組合成像梨形的縮略。由人工香料[[乙酸異戊酯|乙酸異戊酯]]和[[乙酸乙酯|乙酸乙酯]]組成：前者賦予香蕉的味道，後者是梨的味道。兩者的[[酯|酯]]用在許多梨和香蕉味甜食中。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/lancashire/food_and_drink/2004/04/27/stockleys_sweets.shtml |title=Retro flavours for Lancastrian sweet teeth |first=Anne-Louise |last=Mazzafiore |work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]] |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |location=[[London|London]] |date=27 April 2004 |accessdate=3 July 2014 |archive-date=2015-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150804024958/http://www.bbc.co.uk/lancashire/food_and_drink/2004/04/27/stockleys_sweets.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stockleyssweets.co.uk/content/how_stockleys_make_their_sweets/ |title=How Stockleys make their sweets |website=Stockley's Sweets |accessdate=3 July 2014 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303202505/http://www.stockleyssweets.co.uk/content/how_stockleys_make_their_sweets/ |archive-date=2016-03-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

